Description copied from class: StandardDefaultsKb
Returns the list-of-values of slot within frame . If the :collection-type of the slot is :list , and only :direct own slots have been asserted, then order is preserved; otherwise, the values are returned in no guaranteed order. Get-slot-values always returns a list of values. If the specified slot has no values, is returned.
